===1.5.2-RC1 (2015-08-01)===
* Change: Auto-complete partial roads when building level-crossings {{en/Development/Design Drafts/Flyspray|6283}} (r27309)
* Fix: Do not rerandomise the town name when only cost-estimating the founding {{en/Development/Design Drafts/Flyspray|6332}} (r27341)
