* Fix: Incorrect owner assignment when adding/removing road/tram to/from bridges {{en/Development/Design Drafts/Flyspray|6317}} (r27313, r27312)
* Fix: Mark infrastructure window dirty in more cases (r27311)
* Fix: Prevent breaking of tram-reversal points by adding more road pieces {{en/Development/Design Drafts/Flyspray|6283}} (r27308)
* Fix: Error message window with manager face failed with GUI zoom {{en/Development/Design Drafts/Flyspray|6259}} (r27307)
* Fix: Account for road-bridges and drive-through-stops in CanFollowRoad {{en/Development/Design Drafts/Flyspray|6320}} (r27306, r27305)
* Fix: Password window layout with GUI zoom {{en/Development/Design Drafts/Flyspray|6321}} (r27304, r27303)
* Fix: Speed-only timetables got assigned times in stations {{en/Development/Design Drafts/Flyspray|6313}} (r27302, r27301)
* Fix: Enforce the company's default service intervals when purchasing another company {{en/Development/Design Drafts/Flyspray|6254}} (r27282, r27281)
* Fix: Cloning/autoreplace/autorenew did not copy custom service intervals (r27280)

